            "id": "D-011",
            "title": "JSONL event log as supplement",
            "decision": "Maintain a JSONL file alongside SQLite for debugging and potential replay.",
            "rationale": "BE-R052 requires an append-only debug log. JSONL is human-readable, grep-friendly, and trivial to implement. It supplements SQLite \u2014 not a replacement.",
